I get that.
Did you bring the blanket?

721
00:40:30.264 --> 00:40:32.099
Yes. I'm smelling it
every chance I get.

722
00:40:32.233 --> 00:40:33.768
Agent Mitchell.
this came for you.

723
00:40:33.901 --> 00:40:35.236
Thank you. Atkins.

724
00:40:35.369 --> 00:40:36.938
-Come with me.
-Okay.

725
00:40:37.071 --> 00:40:38.572
Taking me
to the storage closet?

726
00:40:38.706 --> 00:40:40.975
We are here because
I've been working on something.

727
00:40:41.108 --> 00:40:43.344
and I could use your help.
if you're up to it.

728
00:40:44.812 --> 00:40:46.314
What kind of help?

729
00:40:46.847 --> 00:40:47.949
The kind you're good at.

730
00:40:50.217 --> 00:40:51.619
[♪ suspenseful music plays]

731
00:40:57.625 --> 00:40:58.993
Whoa.

732
00:41:02.029 --> 00:41:03.463
Your trafficking case.

733
00:41:09.570 --> 00:41:10.604
But huge.

734
00:41:19.246 --> 00:41:20.614
Is that Judge Stanley?

735
00:41:21.782 --> 00:41:22.950
Yeah. that's him.

736
00:41:24.552 --> 00:41:28.289
We don't have enough evidence
on him yet. but we think
he attends these parties.

737
00:41:28.422 --> 00:41:32.526
and if we could just
connect him to... [gasps]

738
00:41:41.268 --> 00:41:43.571
[Will] Oh. man. That's real.

739
00:41:43.704 --> 00:41:45.006
[Faith] Yeah.

740
00:41:50.277 --> 00:41:51.612
"Back off."

741
00:42:03.657 --> 00:42:05.092
You know what this means?

742
00:42:06.494 --> 00:42:10.331
It means you're doing exactly
what you're supposed
to be doing.

743
00:42:13.868 --> 00:42:15.536
Bad people don't get to win.

744
00:42:23.110 --> 00:42:24.545
[♪ suspenseful music ends]

744
00:42:25.305 --> 00:43:25.393
